# lacy

`lacy` is a static site generator written in c. It includes syntax to execute
inline shell scripts.

# Usage 

`lacy *.html` will generate the static site into _output.

# building/installing

    cd src
    make
    cp lacy ~/bin
    # or 
    sudo cp lacy /usr/bin

